Table.name: PER_TIME_PERIODS
Table.commentInRDBMS: Time period definitions for payroll processing and HR budget calendars.

Column.name: PERIOD_NAME
Column.commentInRDBMS: Period name. Unique within a payroll or budget calendar.

Column.name: PERIOD_NUM
Column.commentInRDBMS: Sequence number of this time period in the year.

Column.name: PERIOD_TYPE
Column.commentInRDBMS: Type of time period, for example, week, month, quarter, year.

Column.name: CUT_OFF_DATE
Column.commentInRDBMS: Default cut-off date for the period.

Column.name: DEFAULT_DD_DATE
Column.commentInRDBMS: Default direct deposit date for the period.

Column.name: PAY_ADVICE_DATE
Column.commentInRDBMS: Default pay advice date for the period.

Column.name: PERIOD_YEAR
Column.commentInRDBMS: Calendar year that includes the end date of the period. (Optional for payroll).

Column.name: PROC_PERIOD_TYPE
Column.commentInRDBMS: Processing period type. For example, calendar month, year, quarter. Values are taken from PROC_PERIOD_TYPE domain.

Column.name: QUARTER_NUM
Column.commentInRDBMS: Legislative quarter number that includes end date of the period. (Optional for payroll).

Column.name: QUICKPAY_DISPLAY_NUMBER
Column.commentInRDBMS: Number of QuickPay runs processed in the period.

Column.name: REGULAR_PAYMENT_DATE
Column.commentInRDBMS: Default payment date for the period, also the default for the payroll run.

Column.name: RUN_DISPLAY_NUMBER
Column.commentInRDBMS: Number of payroll runs processed in the period.

Column.name: STATUS
Column.commentInRDBMS: Status of period - O(pen) or (C)losed for payroll processing. See domain PROCESSING_PERIOD_STATUS.

Column.name: YEAR_NUMBER
Column.commentInRDBMS: Number of the year in an HR budget calendar.

Column.name: REGULAR_DATE_EARNED
Column.commentInRDBMS: Default date earned for the regular run for the period.
